      • addPresentation

        boolean addPresentation​(Presentation presentation)
                 throws SessionException
        Adds a new presentation to the session
        Parameters:
        presentation - instance to be inserted. The insertion order defines the initial order in which presentations will be performed
        Returns:
        1. true if the presentation was inserted
        2. false if the presentation already exists
        Throws:
        SessionException -
        1. if the @param presentation is null
        2. if the @link{IPesentation presentation} exceed session maximum duration
        3. if the @link{IPesentation presentation} exceed the maximum time duration for the session
